commit.message:
emit-rtl.c (init_emit_once): Call INIT_EXPANDERS.

        * emit-rtl.c (init_emit_once): Call INIT_EXPANDERS.
        * cpplib.h: Protect from multiple inclusions.
        * cpplib.c: Fix minor formatting problems.

From-SVN: r22937
